review.description: Got a Rump Roast from SoL at the DG Farmer's Market and it was SUPER GREAT!!!!! The roast was very lean and made an awesome Italian Beef cooked in the Crock Pot  (link to recipe: http://allrecipes.com/Recipe/Slow-Cooker-Italian-Beef-for-Sandwiches/Detail.aspx)
review.author: Donna F.
